'''Tutlayin tiznasin''' neɣ '''Taznast''' (s [[tifinaɣ]]: '''ⵜⴰⵣⵏⴰⵙⵜ''') neɣ '''Taznat''' (s [[tifinaɣ]]: '''ⵜⴰⵣⵏⴰⵜ''') d yiwen n umur seg [[tutlayin timaziɣin n ugafa]]. Llan ugar n 6 n yimelyan n yimdanen i yettmeslayen s [[tutlayt|tutlayin]] tiznasin, tutlayin-a ṭṭfent tajumma meqqren di tmura n [[Tamazɣa|tmazɣa]] am [[Ameṛṛuk|Umeṛṛuk]], [[Lezzayer]], [[Tunes]] yakk d [[Libya]].

Taznast d yiwet seg kṛad (3) n tegrawin [[tutlayin timaziɣin|timaziɣin]] meqqren yellan deg [[Tafriqt n Ugafa|Tferka n Ugafa]], nettat yakk d [[Iẓnagen|teẓnagt]] d [[Imṣmuden|yimesmuden]].

== Tutlayin tiznasin ==
Taznast tegber seg waṭas n tutlayin, igan: 
* '''[[Tarifit]]''': ttmeslayen-tt deg ugafa n Umeṛṛuk, tegber seg tantaliwin-a:
** Tarifit tutrimt: ttmeslayen-tt yimezdaɣ n [[Tijdit (Lḥusima)|Tijdit]] d tamiwin i d-as-yezzin.
** Tarifit talemmast: ttmeslayen-tt yimezdaɣ n tamiwin n [[Nnaḍur (Arrif)|Nnaḍur]] d [[Driwec]].
** Tarifit n Yiznassen: ttmeslayen-tt yimezdaɣ n [[Berkan]] yakk d [[Ikebdanen]], dɣa tantala-ayi tettumeggez di kra n tikwal d tutlayt s yiman-is.
** [[Taznast n usamer n Umeṛṛuk]]: ttmeslayen-tt di tama n [[Agezdu n Jrada|Jrada]].

* '''[[Tamaziɣt n Waṭlas Alemmas asemran]]''': ttmeslayen-tt yimezdaɣ n tlemmast-tasemrant n [[Ameṛṛuk|Umeṛṛuk]], tga d amur seg [[tutlayin timaziɣin n waṭlas]]. 
* '''[[Tutlayin tiznasin n utaram n Lezzayer]]''': 
** Tamaziɣt n [[Dehra]] yakk d [[Warsnis]], gar-asent [[Tutlayt tacenwit|tacenwit]] d [[Tidikelt (tantala)|tmaziɣt n tdikelt]].
** [[Tamaziɣt n waṭlas ablidi|Tamaziɣt n Waṭlas Ablidi]]: ttmeslayen-tt di tama n [[Mettijet|Metticet]]. 
** [[Tamaziɣt n Wat Snus]]: ttmeslayen yis yimaziɣen n [[At Snus]], tettumeggez d tantala n [[Tarifit|trifit]]. 
* '''[[Tacawit]]''': ttmeslayen-tt [[Icawiyen|Yicawiyen]] deg tama n [[Awras]] deg usamer n [[Lezzayer]].
